Package org.treetank.service.xml.xpath.filter Description

Package filter

Contains all additional XPath filters or axis that work like filters.

Make sure either extend AbstractFilter and implements IFilter, if the filter is a real node filter or extend AbstractAxis, if the filter is working like an axis.
